edu.udel.cis.vsl.sarl.object.common

Class SimpleSequence<T extends SymbolicExpression>

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.udel.cis.vsl.sarl.object.common.CommonSymbolicObject
      • edu.udel.cis.vsl.sarl.object.common.SimpleSequence<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - the kind of symbolic expressions that will be put in the collection
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    SymbolicObject, SymbolicSequence<T>, java.lang.Iterable<T>

    public class SimpleSequence<T extends SymbolicExpression>
extends CommonSymbolicObject
implements SymbolicSequence<T>
    Implementation based on arrays. The entire array is copied with every operation. Performance can be good for small sized.
